external_references.description: Symantec Threat Hunter Team. (2023, July 18). FIN8 Uses Revamped Sardonic Backdoor to Deliver Noberus Ransomware. Retrieved August 9, 2023.

description: [FIN8](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0061) has deployed ransomware such as [Ragnar Locker](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0481), White Rabbit, and attempted to execute Noberus on compromised networks.(Citation: Symantec FIN8 Jul 2023)
